<GameData>
	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_FIREWORKS_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Fireworks!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_FIREWORKS_CHOICE_1_HELP">
			<Text>To celebrate the WLTKD, there was a huge firework display during the evening. Citizens came from far and wide to see it. Gain 2 [ICON_HAPPINESS_1] Happiness for {5_Turns}.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_PLAYER_EVENT_FOREIGNAID_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Foreign Aid</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_PLAYER_EVENT_FOREIGNAID_HELP">
			<Text>Our country is having a real rough time. I suggest to swallow our pride and appeal for foreign aid and charity money. </Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_FOREIGNAID_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Let's try to get whatever we can, even if it worsens our reputation.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_FOREIGNAID_CHOICE_1_HELP">
			<Text>{1_YieldCost}. {2_InstantYield}</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_FOREIGNAID_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>We will get out of this ourselves.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_FOREIGNAID_CHOICE_2_HELP">
			<Text>Gain nothing.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_HARBORTRADE_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Harbor Trade</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_HARBORTRADE_HELP">
			<Text>The local harbor is flourishing with trade and now foreign merchants are asking to establish a branch office here. However we only have enough place for one of them: </Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_HARBORTRADE_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Merchants who bring new tools and studies are welcomed here!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_HARBORTRADE_CHOICE_1_HELP">
			<Text>Harbor provides +1 [ICON_RESEARCH] Science.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_HARBORTRADE_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>Merchants who bring in cultural artifacts and art are welcomed here!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_HARBORTRADE_CHOICE_2_HELP">
			<Text>Harbor provides +1 [ICON_CULTURE] Culture.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_HARBORTRADE_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Merchants who bring in treasures and riches are welcomed here!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_HARBORTRADE_CHOICE_3_HELP">
			<Text>Harbor provides +2 [ICON_GOLD] Gold.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_COOLSUMMER_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Summertime, And The Weather Is Hot</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_COOLSUMMER_HELP">
			<Text>This summer is particularly hot and the people surrounding you are fighting with the heat. Your advisor suggests to share some of the cool drinks that your majesty likes, but this would require a large expedition to fetch ice. What do we do?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_COOLSUMMER_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Organise a team to go up into the mountains. Let the World know of my generosity.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_COOLSUMMER_CHOICE_1_HELP">
			<Text>Expend {1_YieldCost} for {4_GPChange} and {5_Turns} of WLTKD.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_COOLSUMMER_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>Tell them this is a heavenly punishment, brought about by their sloth! Only if they work hard will the heat go away.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_COOLSUMMER_CHOICE_2_HELP">
			<Text>Utilise your authority over Religion to expend {1_YieldCost} to gain {2_InstantYield}.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_COOLSUMMER_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Organise a team to go out onto the ice shelf. Let the World know of my generosity.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_COOLSUMMER_CHOICE_3_HELP">
			<Text>Expend {1_YieldCost} for {5_Turns} of WLTKD.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_COOLSUMMER_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>We shall have to accept that our projects will be delayed this summer.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_COOLSUMMER_CHOICE_4_HELP">
			<Text>Lose {1_YieldCost} in the City.</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>
